metadata.name: 1 in a million.
metadata.description: Standing in awe at the beautiful neons of Chinatown Sydney I found someone, Cold and hiding from the weather under their umbrella they were in line starring at the lights, Wondering off into a different world. I got this shot quickly before the line moved but when I see it I wonder what this person did afterwards, What life they life, what life everyone lives? For 1 moment we starred off into the same beautiful lights but it'll never happen again because as similar as we are. We are all 1 in a million.
